data.description: Welcome to this stunning home. As you enter you are welcomed with a mudroom to take off your shoes and relax. The main level offers an expansive open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the family room and dining room. The kitchen boasts a charming Classic Retro electric range and refrigerator for a touch of nostalgia. Adjacent to this, you'll discover a cozy living room with a fireplace, and a generously sized first-floor office and workout space. As you walk down the hall you will find a full bathroom and a separate laundry room with newer appliances. Venture upstairs to find 3 bedrooms with a loft area and another full bathroom. Beyond the interior, the outdoor space of this home offers an outdoor oasis with a wrap-around deck, a gazebo, and an above-ground pool, not to mention the convenience of two driveways and a one-car garage.
